    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, original shine and no scratches, dings, or chips whatsoever. Inside, the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling new with no signs of wear on the leather upholstery or carpets. Every mechanical and electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is exceptionally clean. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the dealership.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
