      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It's spotless inside and out, runs like a dream, and is basically as close to brand new as you can get. Come check it out, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
