    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD3S Mazda RX-7 is a definitive example of the front-midship, rear-drive philosophy. Powered by the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW, the power delivery remains seamless with optimal boost pressure across the powerband. The drivetrain features a robust five-speed manual paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry is factory-spec double-wishbone, offering telepathic turn-in. Meticulously maintained with zero vacuum leaks and excellent compression health, this chassis represents a rare, unmolested survivor in collector-grade condition.",
